# Default command-line arguments for prometheus-node-exporter.
# These are passed directly to /usr/bin/node_exporter.
#
# Common options:
#   --web.listen-address=":9100"      (default)
#   --web.telemetry-path="/metrics"   (default)
#   --log.level="info"                debug, info, warn, error
#   --log.format="logfmt"             logfmt, json
#   --collector.disable-defaults      disable all default collectors
#   --collector.<name>                enable a specific collector
#
# Run "node_exporter --help" for the full option list.
#
# Due to shell escaping, to pass backslashes for regexes you need to
# double them (\\d for \d). Under systemd you need to double again
# (\\\\d to mean \d), and escape newlines too.
ARGS=""
